Tanzanian artist Diamond Platinumz has rekindled his love with baby mama Zari Hassan a day after publicly insinuating a possible break up.Diamond flew to South Africa and posted photos and videos capturing cosy moments with his wife Zari and their children Tiffah and NillanHe captioned the photos&nbsp;that he abhors gossip.The singer had on Monday caused a social media storm after posting a photo of Zari in a spa pool with a man male in a compromising position.Zari quickly shared more photos of the spa date, explaining the circumstance of the date and slamming the spread of false information about her.The couple quickly deleted both their posts until Tuesday when Diamond shared a series of photos which he tagged Zari.